➜江西诗人时差先生：落叶
http://www.sohu.com/a/416771886_100115135	49331
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200906/11213a25317c41938e80ce4b2fc447ef.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>落叶</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/时差先生 </strong> </p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一片片落叶</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">潇潇而下</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">红的 黄的 浅蓝的 酱紫的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">静静的睡了一地</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">七彩斑斓 艳丽似火</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">秋已殇</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">马路上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一位维吾尔族的妇女</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在打扫秋之落叶</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">背上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还裹着一个三岁的娃</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200906/f982ca7a551c47fc97e653bba488a319.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
